comment: Amazing! Deep caramel and vanilla. Lots of wood

Exceptional nose -  cherries and light spice, very inviting. 

Palate is medicinal with notes of cherry and dark chocolate. Light and spicy. 

Smooth finish, very well done.
One hell of a bourbon with notes of caramel, vanilla, chocolate, cherry, corn, oak, pepper, cinnamon, mint, cloves, maple syrup, and pecan pie.
